snippet.title: Ragini Dwivedi Wardrobe Malfunction Uncut At SIIMA Awards

localized.description:
Ragini Dwivedi Wardrobe Malfunction Uncut At SIIMA Awards - Last year at SIIMA awards, southern sensation Ragini Dwivedi suffered wardrobe malfunction while performing onstage. Ragini was wearing a black sheer top underneath which she had worn a red coloured blouse. While shaking a leg onstage, the inner layer stooped down revealing more than she intended to.
